  "task": "# Relay stage 1: Ideate\nTask: restarted-task-shows-two-active-stages\nWorking directory: /tmp/nix-shell.DMruMz/visual-relay/wt/76dad813448f/plan-20260701181255/restarted-task-shows-two-active-stages\n\n## Task input\n# Restarted Task Shows Two Active Stages\n\nI opted to restart a task rather than resume, and when it restarted, it showed multiple active (green) stages. Fix.\n\n## Manifest\n(not set yet)\n\n## Task context\n### Screenshot 2026-07-01 at 9.59.05\u202fAM.png (210414 bytes, not inlined)\n\n## Prior stages\n\n\nEnd your reply with a single fenced ```json block, nothing after it, matching: { \"summary\": string, \"options\": string[] }",
